original: 22. During what years were you active in Newsies fandom? (Please write YYYY to YYYY; please write YYYY to Present if you are currently active)
notes: Free text from the `period_active` field was standardized into a machine readable-format. @ Distinct periods of activity were seperated with a semi-colon (;) (i.e the entry 1992-1995;2002-2005 indivates the individul was active both between 1992 and 1995 and between 2002 and 2005, but not between 1995 and 2002.) @ Duration is described using a consistent format for multi-year periods: YYYY-YYYY @ Single year formats are left as a single number: YYYY @ Times indicating "present" for fandom participation was simplified to 2021, since this was the end of the survery period. @ Any description indicating uncertainty has been removed (i.e. 2012ish becomes 2012) @ If users specified a period of particular activity, this has been used as the primary period @ Notes about "sleeper fandom" and "on hiatus" have been removed
